description:
&lt;p&gt;The Public Involvement team is looking for an experienced and confident Public Involvement professional to support the Public Involvement team in West Sussex to deliver high quality public involvement across West Sussex CCG.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will have significant experience of operational public involvement, including the use of a range of methodologies. Sound knowledge of the principles and guidance related to public involvement is essential, as is experience of working with diverse groups and communities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to work collaboratively with a range of partners, including the statutory sector, voluntary and community sector, clinicians and patient groups is also key to the role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be confident in working independently and leading public groups, training and events, whilst also working effectively as part of a cross Sussex team. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information please contact Renee Dickinson, Public Involvement Lead- West Sussex CCG&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ph: 07876 843166  or e-mail: renee.dickinson@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
